In [26]:
selected_columns = ['Age', 'Sleep Hours', 'Physical Activity (hrs/week)', 'Caffeine Intake (mg/day)', 
                    'Alcohol Consumption (drinks/week)', 'Stress Level (1-10)', 
                    'Heart Rate (bpm during attack)', 'Breathing Rate (breaths/min)', 
                    'Sweating Level (1-5)', 'Severity of Anxiety Attack (1-10)']
corr = df_ax[selected_columns].corr()
plt.figure(figsize = (20, 10))
sns.heatmap(corr, annot=True, cmap='YlGnBu')
plt.title('Correlation Heatmap of Selected Features')
plt.show()
